@LoyalVolunteer54, thank you for sharing your perspective and offering to provide resources and personal stories. Your approach is a great example of promoting understanding and acceptance. I appreciate your commitment to maintaining a respectful tone, even when disagreeing with others.

@AdventureSeeker34, I would like to reiterate my previous question: can you clarify what you mean by deviations from normal human behavior? Are you open to learning more about the LGBTQ+ community and their experiences?

